Dialogue: 2,0:00:18.68,0:00:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和上司葵课长出差去了 虽然葵课长人长得漂亮工作做的又好...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:29.44,0:00:34.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对我这样不成熟的社员却很严厉... 不要出差错扯后腿还好
Dialogue: 2,0:00:42.27,0:00:44.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}弊社的云端服务是这样的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:45.55,0:00:46.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:49.00,0:00:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个...
Dialogue: 2,0:00:51.63,0:00:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊...是这样的
Dialogue: 2,0:00:58.67,0:01:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:02.35,0:01:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}弊社是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:01:06.57,0:01:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你你你
Dialogue: 2,0:01:12.10,0:01:16.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们并不想更换目前使用的系统
Dialogue: 2,0:01:18.97,0:01:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}与其说是没有必要更换新系统
Dialogue: 2,0:01:25.50,0:01:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们必须要知道你们的优点
Dialogue: 2,0:01:29.17,0:01:29.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个...
Dialogue: 2,0:01:33.29,0:01:34.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}差不多该走了
Dialogue: 2,0:01:38.70,0:01:40.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们社的系统特徵是
Dialogue: 2,0:01:41.18,0:01:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}强大的安全性
Dialogue: 2,0:01:43.96,0:01:49.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和原本使用的系统相比强化了3万的安全系数
Dialogue: 2,0:01:49.55,0:01:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}并且拥有更快速的网路环境
Dialogue: 2,0:01:54.80,0:02:02.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}追求人性化的用户介面设计适合广泛的年龄层使用
Dialogue: 2,0:02:05.37,0:02:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}确实安全系数对我们来说是很重要的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:13.32,0:02:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}而且能让年长的社员轻易使用也是很好的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:20.82,0:02:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}请务必考虑使用弊社的系统
Dialogue: 2,0:02:34.48,0:02:36.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天多谢了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:37.00,0:02:39.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢
Dialogue: 2,0:02:44.90,0:02:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长
Dialogue: 2,0:02:45.68,0:02:46.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢您了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:46.74,0:02:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天课长不在的话
Dialogue: 2,0:02:48.33,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}生意一定不会成功的
Dialogue: 2,0:02:52.00,0:02:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你也差不多应该要独当一面了
Dialogue: 2,0:02:58.14,0:03:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}总不能每次都带你出差
Dialogue: 2,0:03:02.00,0:03:04.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起我会努力的
Dialogue: 2,0:03:05.95,0:03:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托你了
Dialogue: 2,0:03:11.00,0:03:13.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}回饭店还太早
Dialogue: 2,0:03:13.65,0:03:15.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喝两杯去
Dialogue: 2,0:03:15.35,0:03:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是 务必让我同行
Dialogue: 2,0:03:25.62,0:03:26.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以我说
Dialogue: 2,0:03:26.85,0:03:28.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你
Dialogue: 2,0:03:28.82,0:03:31.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}应该自信点
Dialogue: 2,0:03:34.09,0:03:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自信点
Dialogue: 2,0:03:37.03,0:03:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以你会被生意对像瞧不起 懂？
Dialogue: 2,0:03:43.88,0:03:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}装的也行
Dialogue: 2,0:03:48.15,0:03:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要有自信
Dialogue: 2,0:03:50.44,0:03:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说话才有说服力
Dialogue: 2,0:03:56.95,0:04:00.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没什么自信
Dialogue: 2,0:04:01.15,0:04:02.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:04.60,0:04:08.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}精神寄托什么的
Dialogue: 2,0:04:13.42,0:04:14.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有吗！
Dialogue: 2,0:04:15.93,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:17.81,0:04:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这么说来...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:19.65,0:04:21.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个...
Dialogue: 2,0:04:23.83,0:04:24.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}難波
Dialogue: 2,0:04:25.32,0:04:25.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是是
Dialogue: 2,0:04:26.17,0:04:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刚才看手表了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:04:30.10,0:04:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说的就是这个
Dialogue: 2,0:04:33.60,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}差不多饭店的时间
Dialogue: 2,0:04:36.70,0:04:40.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没事的饭店就在车站前
Dialogue: 2,0:04:41.10,0:04:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}末班车没了也没事
Dialogue: 2,0:04:44.40,0:04:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要喝到末班车来吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么可能喝那么久？但是我要喝
Dialogue: 2,0:04:48.80,0:04:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是继续喝
Dialogue: 2,0:04:52.23,0:04:53.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喝
Dialogue: 2,0:04:58.71,0:05:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没了嘛
Dialogue: 2,0:05:02.00,0:05:03.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}给我喝
Dialogue: 2,0:05:14.39,0:05:15.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不好意思
Dialogue: 2,0:05:17.15,0:05:19.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再开一瓶啤酒
Dialogue: 2,0:05:28.18,0:05:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长
Dialogue: 2,0:05:29.21,0:05:31.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没事吧，这里走这里
Dialogue: 2,0:05:36.37,0:05:37.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}先坐著休息一下
Dialogue: 2,0:05:38.80,0:05:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}走到椅子那里去
Dialogue: 2,0:05:41.61,0:05:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}哪里？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:42.41,0:05:43.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里这里
Dialogue: 2,0:05:48.26,0:05:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说了没事
Dialogue: 2,0:05:50.84,0:05:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}完全没问题别担心我
Dialogue: 2,0:05:54.75,0:05:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没事没事
Dialogue: 2,0:05:56.16,0:05:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我没喝醉
Dialogue: 2,0:05:58.36,0:05:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是这样吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:05:59.17,0:06:00.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对，我没问题
Dialogue: 2,0:06:03.47,0:06:04.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长
Dialogue: 2,0:06:04.27,0:06:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的没问题？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:06.62,0:06:07.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没问题
Dialogue: 2,0:06:07.97,0:06:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真没有问题
Dialogue: 2,0:06:10.91,0:06:11.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没问题
Dialogue: 2,0:06:12.15,0:06:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是吗？嗯！
Dialogue: 2,0:06:20.15,0:06:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长，话说回来
Dialogue: 2,0:06:22.47,0:06:29.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的房间是这饭店的另外一个屋子对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:06:32.00,0:06:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只定了一个房
Dialogue: 2,0:06:34.82,0:06:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 2,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以说
Dialogue: 2,0:06:41.79,0:06:42.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个房间
Dialogue: 2,0:06:43.70,0:06:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和我一起住
Dialogue: 2,0:06:46.72,0:06:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不不不这样不好吧！
Dialogue: 2,0:06:49.04,0:06:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}相部屋什么的
Dialogue: 2,0:06:53.95,0:06:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长是女性
Dialogue: 2,0:06:57.07,0:06:58.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}两个人相部屋什么的...
Dialogue: 2,0:06:58.39,0:07:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说了没问题
Dialogue: 2,0:07:01.02,0:07:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说可以就是可以！
Dialogue: 2,0:07:05.47,0:07:07.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长你在摸哪里...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:10.90,0:07:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:14.12,0:07:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}装什么呢
Dialogue: 2,0:07:22.45,0:07:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难波你该不会是...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:27.35,0:07:28.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}童贞？
Dialogue: 2,0:07:28.60,0:07:29.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不不...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:30.24,0:07:31.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说什么呢突然...
Dialogue: 2,0:07:31.67,0:07:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊哈哈
Dialogue: 2,0:07:32.66,0:07:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么突然说这种事
Dialogue: 2,0:07:35.47,0:07:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样啊~
Dialogue: 2,0:07:37.72,0:07:40.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不是 我没有 别瞎说
Dialogue: 2,0:07:40.90,0:07:45.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}欸~~~~~
Dialogue: 2,0:07:46.25,0:07:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}原来是处男~
Dialogue: 2,0:07:49.10,0:07:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真不是别瞎说啊
Dialogue: 2,0:07:54.59,0:07:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}处男什么的...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:03.57,0:08:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那...
Dialogue: 2,0:08:05.67,0:08:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我来帮你毕业吧
Dialogue: 2,0:08:35.35,0:08:37.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你怎么当真了啊
Dialogue: 2,0:08:38.17,0:08:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}跟你开玩笑呢
Dialogue: 2,0:08:44.03,0:08:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}开玩笑呢！拜托了
Dialogue: 2,0:08:47.37,0:08:48.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托了！
Dialogue: 2,0:08:48.89,0:08:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托了！
Dialogue: 2,0:08:53.05,0:08:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:08:54.35,0:08:55.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托了！
Dialogue: 2,0:08:59.15,0:09:00.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你硬了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:01.27,0:09:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我硬了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:06.85,0:09:09.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真糟糕，欸嘿嘿
Dialogue: 2,0:09:09.86,0:09:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么变这么硬
Dialogue: 2,0:09:19.52,0:09:21.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}身体太僵硬了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:23.24,0:09:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:27.31,0:09:28.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我知道了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:31.82,0:09:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一点点而已哦
Dialogue: 2,0:09:38.17,0:09:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是因为喝醉了才做的
Dialogue: 2,0:09:42.64,0:09:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喝醉了所以做一点
Dialogue: 2,0:09:46.08,0:09:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是一点的话也不是不行
Dialogue: 2,0:09:50.90,0:09:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有劳了
Dialogue: 2,0:09:51.83,0:09:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:53.90,0:09:56.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这么想要吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:09:56.25,0:09:56.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托了
Dialogue: 2,0:10:15.29,0:10:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}第一次被这样摸吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:18.37,0:10:19.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是，是第一次...
Dialogue: 2,0:10:24.62,0:10:25.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}心情如何
Dialogue: 2,0:10:27.32,0:10:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:10:30.81,0:10:32.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:32.47,0:10:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喜欢这样？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:34.85,0:10:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好爽
Dialogue: 2,0:10:36.17,0:10:38.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只是这样就舒服了吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:38.39,0:10:39.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:10:48.79,0:10:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在发抖呢
Dialogue: 2,0:10:51.10,0:10:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直想要被这样做啊？
Dialogue: 2,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想被摸
Dialogue: 2,0:11:04.04,0:11:06.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}越来越硬了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:07.66,0:11:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}该不会快射了吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:12.30,0:11:13.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说了只帮你做一点
Dialogue: 2,0:11:14.78,0:11:15.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很抱歉
Dialogue: 2,0:11:21.47,0:11:22.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害
Dialogue: 2,0:11:24.23,0:11:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊要射了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:25.94,0:11:27.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要射了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:28.35,0:11:33.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要射了
Dialogue: 2,0:11:34.85,0:11:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}认真的？等等
Dialogue: 2,0:11:43.56,0:11:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}等等
Dialogue: 2,0:11:45.95,0:11:47.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}！什么？
Dialogue: 2,0:11:59.11,0:12:01.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这就射了？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:02.50,0:12:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是不是有点快？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:07.05,0:12:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射的好多
Dialogue: 2,0:12:09.89,0:12:13.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}弄的满手都是，还射到空中了刚才
Dialogue: 2,0:12:14.03,0:12:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起实在太舒服了
Dialogue: 2,0:12:17.08,0:12:19.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}已经可以了吧
Dialogue: 2,0:12:20.91,0:12:22.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还没好
Dialogue: 2,0:12:22.06,0:12:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还不行
Dialogue: 2,0:12:23.93,0:12:25.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样就可以了吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:28.78,0:12:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还硬的呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:31.60,0:12:33.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才刚射完呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:34.96,0:12:37.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样就好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还想要多做点
Dialogue: 2,0:12:40.30,0:12:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}更多？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:42.27,0:12:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}例如呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:50.27,0:12:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}例如这样？
Dialogue: 2,0:12:58.87,0:13:01.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没被这样做过吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:13:01.77,0:13:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有，这是第一次
Dialogue: 2,0:13:19.94,0:13:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}帮你弄乾净
Dialogue: 2,0:13:33.24,0:13:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又硬帮了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:42.65,0:13:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太舒服了
Dialogue: 2,0:13:54.45,0:13:57.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}女人的嘴很舒服吧
Dialogue: 2,0:13:58.72,0:14:00.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舒...啊啊啊...服
Dialogue: 2,0:14:03.51,0:14:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}女人的嘴很柔软
Dialogue: 2,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又温暖你看
Dialogue: 2,0:14:10.70,0:14:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}会上瘾的哦
Dialogue: 2,0:14:13.28,0:14:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:21.94,0:14:24.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太爽了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:33.92,0:14:36.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不想做更多吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:14:36.42,0:14:37.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托了
Dialogue: 2,0:14:40.77,0:14:42.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}床上躺好
Dialogue: 2,0:14:45.45,0:14:46.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长
Dialogue: 2,0:14:53.07,0:14:54.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘿咻
Dialogue: 2,0:14:58.52,0:15:00.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那我...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:00.51,0:15:02.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要把难波吃了唷？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:04.43,0:15:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托了
Dialogue: 2,0:15:09.47,0:15:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:10.49,0:15:11.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:12.80,0:15:14.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想被你吃
Dialogue: 2,0:15:34.28,0:15:35.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}kiss也是第一次？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:36.69,0:15:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小时候有过...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:41.38,0:15:42.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:15:43.24,0:15:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是初吻了啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:15:45.77,0:15:48.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是成人的kiss是第一次
Dialogue: 2,0:15:59.70,0:16:03.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样的kiss是第一次？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:25.20,0:16:26.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说啊
Dialogue: 2,0:16:28.51,0:16:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从刚才就很在意一件事
Dialogue: 2,0:16:34.32,0:16:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难波你的乳头怎么这么大的？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:37.52,0:16:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:38.43,0:16:39.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这是因为...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:44.70,0:16:47.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也不知道为什么...
Dialogue: 2,0:16:49.91,0:16:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乳头勃起的很厉害
Dialogue: 2,0:16:55.64,0:16:58.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自己做的时候摸了对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种事
Dialogue: 2,0:17:00.16,0:17:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这种事
Dialogue: 2,0:17:02.16,0:17:03.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:05.74,0:17:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一边自慰一边搓自己乳头了吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:09.02,0:17:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那个...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:14.83,0:17:17.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}所以才变得这么大的吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:19.58,0:17:20.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没有的事...
Dialogue: 2,0:17:21.74,0:17:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊啊好爽
Dialogue: 2,0:17:23.42,0:17:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乳头很舒服嘛！
Dialogue: 2,0:17:31.07,0:17:35.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不说实话的话不摸了哦
Dialogue: 2,0:17:38.52,0:17:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想被摸
Dialogue: 2,0:17:41.03,0:17:42.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自己平常经常摸吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:44.98,0:17:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自己一边摸乳头一边打飞机对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:17:49.20,0:17:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是一边摸乳头一边打飞机的
Dialogue: 2,0:17:54.66,0:17:55.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从实招来了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:04.08,0:18:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是好孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:18:07.60,0:18:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}色小孩
Dialogue: 2,0:18:14.51,0:18:17.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是色小孩
Dialogue: 2,0:18:20.71,0:18:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乳头被舔了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:25.20,0:18:27.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乳头...被舔了...
Dialogue: 2,0:18:43.53,0:18:45.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想像过这种事对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:48.75,0:18:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想像这种事打飞机了
Dialogue: 2,0:18:53.48,0:18:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是坏孩子
Dialogue: 2,0:18:56.59,0:18:58.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}期待著啊？
Dialogue: 2,0:18:58.65,0:18:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起
Dialogue: 2,0:19:00.42,0:19:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}什么时候开始？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:02.55,0:19:04.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从入社开始一直...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:04.83,0:19:06.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从那个时候开始？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:06.00,0:19:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}用课长想像著
Dialogue: 2,0:19:13.71,0:19:16.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从那个时候就在想这种事情？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:16.21,0:19:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起
Dialogue: 2,0:19:22.46,0:19:24.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那现在很幸福呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:19:24.62,0:19:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很幸福的...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:31.91,0:19:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说"课长我很幸福"来听听
Dialogue: 2,0:19:34.85,0:19:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...我很幸福...
Dialogue: 2,0:19:39.30,0:19:40.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好好说
Dialogue: 2,0:19:43.22,0:19:46.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...我好幸福...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:16.36,0:20:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}表情真丢人
Dialogue: 2,0:20:21.42,0:20:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}兴奋了
Dialogue: 2,0:20:27.39,0:20:30.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再给我多看点你那丢人的表情
Dialogue: 2,0:20:32.66,0:20:35.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你很舒服呢
Dialogue: 2,0:20:40.84,0:20:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}上下都想赶快弄的湿答答呢
Dialogue: 2,0:20:44.98,0:20:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是...想要...
Dialogue: 2,0:20:58.35,0:21:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}像这样，你看
Dialogue: 2,0:21:04.66,0:21:07.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}有鸡儿等著想要被摸
Dialogue: 2,0:21:07.69,0:21:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是...等好久了
Dialogue: 2,0:21:41.37,0:21:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那...最喜欢的乳头
Dialogue: 2,0:21:44.98,0:21:48.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一边被舔一边套弄会更舒服吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:07.80,0:22:09.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:09.44,0:22:11.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我好幸福...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:20.62,0:22:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很开心呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:21.73,0:22:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很开心的！
Dialogue: 2,0:22:23.17,0:22:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让你更开心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:27.96,0:22:30.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被课长舔著很开心
Dialogue: 2,0:22:39.57,0:22:43.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很开心？ 感谢的话语呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:22:43.03,0:22:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢！谢谢！很开心呢？谢谢~~~
Dialogue: 2,0:22:50.15,0:22:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不行
Dialogue: 2,0:22:52.16,0:22:54.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么这样...
Dialogue: 2,0:22:56.16,0:22:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:09.64,0:23:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好好把腰动起来
Dialogue: 2,0:23:13.10,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不能放开吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:18.36,0:23:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}放开就射了不是吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:20.33,0:23:22.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}唔唔...好想射...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:23.00,0:23:24.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这么想射？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:28.70,0:23:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要自己动来动去
Dialogue: 2,0:23:32.75,0:23:34.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的手好舒服...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:38.36,0:23:40.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直被握著...
Dialogue: 2,0:23:45.92,0:23:47.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不放到嘴里吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:23:50.02,0:23:51.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想放进去...
Dialogue: 2,0:24:10.42,0:24:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}欸 忍耐汁（尿道球腺液）
Dialogue: 2,0:24:20.25,0:24:22.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}流了好多忍耐汁
Dialogue: 2,0:24:26.04,0:24:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忍耐很久了
Dialogue: 2,0:24:33.40,0:24:35.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天一整天就像约会呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:24:36.24,0:24:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不只是今天啊
Dialogue: 2,0:24:54.71,0:24:56.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要射了要射了
Dialogue: 2,0:25:05.60,0:25:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不行
Dialogue: 2,0:25:11.22,0:25:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不想摸我吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:14.70,0:25:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想...想摸...
Dialogue: 2,0:25:18.60,0:25:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那给你摸，过来
Dialogue: 2,0:25:36.67,0:25:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么样，胸部
Dialogue: 2,0:25:38.73,0:25:40.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好软
Dialogue: 2,0:25:40.18,0:25:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:42.67,0:25:44.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舒服...
Dialogue: 2,0:25:51.87,0:25:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天看我的胸部看到忘我了对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:25:57.27,0:25:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那是因为...
Dialogue: 2,0:25:59.17,0:26:01.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你以为没被发现？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:01.67,0:26:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起...
Dialogue: 2,0:26:04.82,0:26:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}温柔一点
Dialogue: 2,0:26:08.77,0:26:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}摸的方式色情点
Dialogue: 2,0:26:46.35,0:26:48.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天穿了这样的内衣
Dialogue: 2,0:26:50.59,0:26:51.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能看到真好呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:26:51.95,0:26:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的...
Dialogue: 2,0:26:55.19,0:26:56.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好合适...
Dialogue: 2,0:27:13.37,0:27:15.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}摸的方式变色情了
Dialogue: 2,0:27:22.42,0:27:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来
Dialogue: 2,0:27:27.37,0:27:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里也给你摸
Dialogue: 2,0:27:31.42,0:27:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害
Dialogue: 2,0:27:33.92,0:27:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的乳头
Dialogue: 2,0:27:37.24,0:27:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}挺的好直
Dialogue: 2,0:27:39.65,0:27:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以摸吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:05.00,0:28:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服，是因为喝醉了嘛？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:08.84,0:28:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好像变敏感了
Dialogue: 2,0:28:16.64,0:28:18.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}搓它
Dialogue: 2,0:28:19.45,0:28:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}站著了对吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:28:37.58,0:28:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对
Dialogue: 2,0:28:41.11,0:28:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对
Dialogue: 2,0:28:42.19,0:28:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是这样
Dialogue: 2,0:29:09.95,0:29:13.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}呐，难波，想舔我的乳头？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:14.16,0:29:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想舔...
Dialogue: 2,0:29:20.67,0:29:22.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:29:25.62,0:29:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的乳头...
Dialogue: 2,0:29:41.71,0:29:43.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真淫荡
Dialogue: 2,0:29:43.98,0:29:45.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对用舌头
Dialogue: 2,0:29:46.03,0:29:47.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样吗？
