Dialogue: 2,0:46:46.77,0:46:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我的小穴很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:53.89,0:46:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以摸胸部吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:46:57.25,0:47:01.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以唷，同时摸，一边摸一边插
Dialogue: 2,0:47:04.46,0:47:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对腰就这样
Dialogue: 2,0:47:06.62,0:47:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么舒服怎么动
Dialogue: 2,0:47:10.71,0:47:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对对对
Dialogue: 2,0:47:13.23,0:47:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在里面勃起的好厉害
Dialogue: 2,0:47:19.34,0:47:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}里面满满的
Dialogue: 2,0:47:33.95,0:47:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太舒服了课长，太舒服了...
Dialogue: 2,0:47:47.26,0:47:49.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我在上面动吧
Dialogue: 2,0:47:49.37,0:47:51.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢...
Dialogue: 2,0:48:17.00,0:48:20.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想像过被这样侵犯对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:22.27,0:48:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被课长
Dialogue: 2,0:48:23.57,0:48:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}侵犯...
Dialogue: 2,0:48:25.01,0:48:27.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想像过...
Dialogue: 2,0:48:27.97,0:48:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是变态呢
Dialogue: 2,0:48:32.12,0:48:35.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我现在好幸福...
Dialogue: 2,0:48:36.17,0:48:38.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真是幸福呢
Dialogue: 2,0:48:55.20,0:48:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}鸡儿全部插进了很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:48:59.90,0:49:00.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很舒服...
Dialogue: 2,0:49:04.23,0:49:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很舒服吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:07.75,0:49:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服...
Dialogue: 2,0:49:09.37,0:49:11.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的小穴好舒服...
Dialogue: 2,0:49:31.15,0:49:33.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我说好之前不准射呢
Dialogue: 2,0:49:34.08,0:49:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好我会忍耐
Dialogue: 2,0:49:36.04,0:49:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好
Dialogue: 2,0:49:49.10,0:49:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}鸡儿的精神很好呢
Dialogue: 2,0:49:52.75,0:49:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}叫的这么大声
Dialogue: 2,0:49:55.50,0:49:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还缓不下来？
Dialogue: 2,0:49:58.92,0:50:00.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}停不下来
Dialogue: 2,0:50:00.07,0:50:01.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}停不下来呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:50:01.85,0:50:02.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}因为是课长...
Dialogue: 2,0:50:02.55,0:50:03.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不行呢
Dialogue: 2,0:50:03.96,0:50:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起
Dialogue: 2,0:50:04.87,0:50:07.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}停不下来真拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 2,0:50:07.87,0:50:09.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,0:50:31.21,0:50:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看
Dialogue: 2,0:50:32.45,0:50:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}鸡儿被吃掉的地方
Dialogue: 2,0:50:39.67,0:50:42.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}记住被小穴吃掉的样子
Dialogue: 2,0:50:42.65,0:50:44.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}记住了...
Dialogue: 2,0:50:56.74,0:50:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去的太厉害要变成笨蛋了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:01.49,0:51:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}里面好热
Dialogue: 2,0:51:03.34,0:51:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好温暖
Dialogue: 2,0:51:07.79,0:51:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害变得好热
Dialogue: 2,0:51:14.02,0:51:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对，要缩紧了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:21.40,0:51:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来这里
Dialogue: 2,0:51:24.05,0:51:25.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来这里
Dialogue: 2,0:51:27.92,0:51:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}侵犯我看看
Dialogue: 2,0:51:31.03,0:51:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}紧贴著呢
Dialogue: 2,0:51:39.32,0:51:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很舒服呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:51:41.12,0:51:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的小穴好舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:51:52.35,0:51:54.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}撞到阴蒂了
Dialogue: 2,0:51:54.63,0:51:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}里面好舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:51:57.45,0:52:00.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}鸡儿撞到阴蒂了
Dialogue: 2,0:52:01.15,0:52:04.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害呢
Dialogue: 2,0:52:04.37,0:52:07.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}做这种事
Dialogue: 2,0:52:23.20,0:52:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喜欢屁股对吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:52:49.47,0:52:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}非常...舒服...
Dialogue: 2,0:53:12.65,0:53:15.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被课长的屁股侵犯了...
Dialogue: 2,0:53:15.39,0:53:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是的呢
Dialogue: 2,0:53:16.72,0:53:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在用屁股侵犯你呢
Dialogue: 2,0:53:20.97,0:53:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}屁股全部被你看光了
Dialogue: 2,0:53:43.22,0:53:43.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好像已经
Dialogue: 2,0:53:50.84,0:53:52.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,0:53:54.35,0:53:56.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难波我要去了
Dialogue: 2,0:53:57.80,0:53:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,0:54:08.64,0:54:11.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我忍住...
Dialogue: 2,0:54:11.84,0:54:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从后面来
Dialogue: 2,0:54:19.50,0:54:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从后面插进来
Dialogue: 2,0:54:27.87,0:54:28.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把内裤掰开
Dialogue: 2,0:54:29.16,0:54:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对插进来
Dialogue: 2,0:54:31.85,0:54:33.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊这样好舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:54:45.54,0:54:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太舒服要射了
Dialogue: 2,0:54:48.65,0:54:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可以
Dialogue: 2,0:55:03.15,0:55:04.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}动起来
Dialogue: 2,0:55:09.44,0:55:11.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的小穴好舒服...
Dialogue: 2,0:55:13.17,0:55:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害的声音
Dialogue: 2,0:55:24.00,0:55:25.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}撞到里面了
Dialogue: 2,0:55:26.81,0:55:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}撞到阴蒂了
Dialogue: 2,0:55:34.30,0:55:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又要去了
Dialogue: 2,0:55:39.01,0:55:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去了
Dialogue: 2,0:56:14.00,0:56:15.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太舒服了...
Dialogue: 2,0:56:22.47,0:56:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可以
Dialogue: 2,0:56:29.49,0:56:30.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服
Dialogue: 2,0:56:31.87,0:56:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不好了
Dialogue: 2,0:56:43.02,0:56:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}阴蒂还要
Dialogue: 2,0:56:47.65,0:56:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好
Dialogue: 2,0:56:49.17,0:56:51.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又撞到阴蒂了
Dialogue: 2,0:57:32.47,0:57:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}腰动了很多呢
Dialogue: 2,0:57:35.68,0:57:37.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}停不下来呢？
Dialogue: 2,0:57:37.98,0:57:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害呢
Dialogue: 2,0:57:42.44,0:57:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,0:58:06.47,0:58:08.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忍耐了很久呢
Dialogue: 2,0:58:11.57,0:58:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想进去？
Dialogue: 2,0:58:13.80,0:58:14.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想射出来？
