Dialogue: 2,0:58:35.52,0:58:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想在哪里射出来？
Dialogue: 2,0:58:46.41,0:58:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的嘴里...
Dialogue: 2,0:58:49.60,0:58:50.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射出来..
Dialogue: 2,0:58:50.82,0:58:53.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}嘴里？
Dialogue: 2,0:58:53.28,0:58:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想在口里射精啊？
Dialogue: 2,0:58:56.39,0:58:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射出来吗？
Dialogue: 2,0:59:05.95,0:59:10.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在嘴里把忍耐了的精液射出来吧？
Dialogue: 2,0:59:11.89,0:59:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又硬了
Dialogue: 2,0:59:15.40,0:59:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射吧
Dialogue: 2,0:59:20.97,0:59:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好淫荡
Dialogue: 2,0:59:23.12,0:59:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长
Dialogue: 2,0:59:24.72,0:59:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我要射了
Dialogue: 2,1:00:27.35,1:00:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射了很多呢
Dialogue: 2,1:00:32.60,1:00:34.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}毕业了呢
Dialogue: 2,1:00:35.45,1:00:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢课长...
Dialogue: 2,1:00:46.62,1:00:49.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我们都流了好多汗呢
Dialogue: 2,1:00:49.94,1:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}洗澡去吧
Dialogue: 2,1:01:06.75,1:01:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刚才射了那么多
Dialogue: 2,1:01:10.72,1:01:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又硬成这样？
Dialogue: 2,1:01:14.17,1:01:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么？
Dialogue: 2,1:01:19.88,1:01:21.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还想要？
Dialogue: 2,1:01:21.57,1:01:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不是...
Dialogue: 2,1:01:31.07,1:01:33.71,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}光是套弄不能满足呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:01:57.96,1:01:58.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...
Dialogue: 2,1:01:58.62,1:02:02.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}才射过现在乳头又挺成这样
Dialogue: 2,1:02:05.05,1:02:07.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一下子就亢奋了？
Dialogue: 2,1:02:08.58,1:02:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忍不住...
Dialogue: 2,1:02:35.67,1:02:38.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舌头多伸点出来
Dialogue: 2,1:02:50.22,1:02:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}学会淫荡的kiss了呢
Dialogue: 2,1:02:58.07,1:03:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里变得怎样了呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:03:04.82,1:03:07.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...好舒服...
Dialogue: 2,1:03:07.70,1:03:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}前端流出忍耐汁了呢
Dialogue: 2,1:03:18.75,1:03:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}变成这样了
Dialogue: 2,1:03:21.52,1:03:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还想射吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:03:23.87,1:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想...
Dialogue: 2,1:03:32.93,1:03:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}赶快多流点出来
Dialogue: 2,1:03:36.38,1:03:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不行？ 还要让你流很多出来
Dialogue: 2,1:03:46.77,1:03:49.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}前面变得好湿
Dialogue: 2,1:03:58.84,1:04:00.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我不行了
Dialogue: 2,1:04:04.28,1:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里也？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:06.26,1:04:07.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么这样...
Dialogue: 2,1:04:08.95,1:04:10.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里也不行了？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:10.82,1:04:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太舒服整个人都不对劲了
Dialogue: 2,1:04:19.38,1:04:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样，根部和
Dialogue: 2,1:04:24.30,1:04:26.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样前后一起
Dialogue: 2,1:04:27.43,1:04:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舒服吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:33.25,1:04:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}从根部这样套弄
Dialogue: 2,1:04:36.70,1:04:38.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样舒服嘛？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:39.57,1:04:42.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样？ 这样呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:44.07,1:04:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么样做好呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:04:49.00,1:04:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么样
Dialogue: 2,1:04:52.57,1:04:54.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}把你弄的湿湿的
Dialogue: 2,1:04:58.62,1:04:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服
Dialogue: 2,1:05:20.76,1:05:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舌头伸出来
Dialogue: 2,1:05:33.95,1:05:37.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舌头前端动一动
Dialogue: 2,1:05:47.92,1:05:49.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舒服吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:05:50.54,1:05:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想去了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:05:53.00,1:05:55.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直想去...
Dialogue: 2,1:06:01.25,1:06:03.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还不可以
Dialogue: 2,1:06:03.84,1:06:05.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:06:07.75,1:06:09.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样好好忍耐住
Dialogue: 2,1:06:11.25,1:06:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忍耐了才会变强
Dialogue: 2,1:06:13.40,1:06:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}学会了很多对吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:06:19.00,1:06:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好痛苦...
Dialogue: 2,1:06:20.77,1:06:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}肿起来了呢
Dialogue: 2,1:06:24.31,1:06:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}肿起来了？
Dialogue: 2,1:06:34.65,1:06:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}肿胀的鸡儿
Dialogue: 2,1:06:36.80,1:06:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}肿胀鸡儿不许射精
Dialogue: 2,1:06:47.37,1:06:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样弄要射了
Dialogue: 2,1:06:56.42,1:06:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再帮你加把火
Dialogue: 2,1:07:04.54,1:07:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}啊
Dialogue: 2,1:07:06.09,1:07:07.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么...
Dialogue: 2,1:07:09.02,1:07:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还不可以
Dialogue: 2,1:07:10.90,1:07:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说了还不可以。对不起
Dialogue: 2,1:07:20.77,1:07:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不想被舔乳头吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:07:23.75,1:07:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想被舔...
