Dialogue: 2,1:32:39.95,1:32:42.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喜欢这样
Dialogue: 2,1:32:43.48,1:32:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乳头勃起了
Dialogue: 2,1:32:48.22,1:32:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对就这样
Dialogue: 2,1:32:56.94,1:32:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:32:59.62,1:33:01.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:33:02.20,1:33:04.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好好看我高潮的样子
Dialogue: 2,1:33:05.75,1:33:07.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看著我
Dialogue: 2,1:33:08.42,1:33:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看著我去好吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:33:15.54,1:33:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去了去了
Dialogue: 2,1:33:20.57,1:33:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}淫荡小穴去了
Dialogue: 2,1:33:38.29,1:33:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}糟糕
Dialogue: 2,1:33:42.60,1:33:43.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不好
Dialogue: 2,1:33:45.00,1:33:46.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}变得湿漉漉的
Dialogue: 2,1:33:46.93,1:33:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你看
Dialogue: 2,1:33:56.40,1:33:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你摸摸看这么湿了
Dialogue: 2,1:34:05.90,1:34:09.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}内裤也好湿了
Dialogue: 2,1:34:22.27,1:34:24.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直流出来了
Dialogue: 2,1:34:31.00,1:34:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}手指伸进去确认
Dialogue: 2,1:34:33.49,1:34:35.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}里面怎么样了
Dialogue: 2,1:34:36.82,1:34:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}放进去了
Dialogue: 2,1:34:40.82,1:34:41.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}慢慢的
Dialogue: 2,1:34:58.90,1:35:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}湿糊糊的对吧
Dialogue: 2,1:35:03.30,1:35:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小穴湿糊糊的
Dialogue: 2,1:35:12.44,1:35:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里用手指扣
Dialogue: 2,1:35:14.69,1:35:16.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里吗
Dialogue: 2,1:35:16.34,1:35:18.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对喜欢这样扣
Dialogue: 2,1:35:28.31,1:35:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服
Dialogue: 2,1:35:31.02,1:35:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是这样
Dialogue: 2,1:35:40.42,1:35:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}旁边也要
Dialogue: 2,1:35:54.47,1:35:56.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要放两根进去了
Dialogue: 2,1:36:10.57,1:36:12.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样对吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:36:19.14,1:36:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}慢慢来
Dialogue: 2,1:36:23.42,1:36:25.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}喜欢这样
Dialogue: 2,1:36:28.85,1:36:30.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}继续
Dialogue: 2,1:36:37.22,1:36:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:37:09.45,1:37:12.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}帮我把内裤脱了
Dialogue: 2,1:37:13.13,1:37:14.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}帮我舔
Dialogue: 2,1:37:14.85,1:37:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}帮我舔乾净
Dialogue: 2,1:37:18.60,1:37:19.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}拜托了
Dialogue: 2,1:37:57.50,1:37:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里敏感
Dialogue: 2,1:38:07.57,1:38:11.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我才刚去过
Dialogue: 2,1:38:13.77,1:38:18.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不可以那里敏感刚去过
Dialogue: 2,1:38:23.20,1:38:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样舔我又要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:38:35.95,1:38:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}去了
Dialogue: 2,1:38:50.59,1:38:53.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你做什么得意忘形的事啊
Dialogue: 2,1:38:59.24,1:39:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谁说可以那样做的
Dialogue: 2,1:39:02.60,1:39:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:39:33.52,1:39:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不准休息
Dialogue: 2,1:39:39.91,1:39:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好好的舔
Dialogue: 2,1:39:41.49,1:39:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对继续
Dialogue: 2,1:39:46.22,1:39:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不然不帮你舔
Dialogue: 2,1:39:48.85,1:39:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:40:22.10,1:40:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好多口水流出来了
Dialogue: 2,1:40:43.76,1:40:46.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}前端变成这样了
Dialogue: 2,1:40:49.31,1:40:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这个？
Dialogue: 2,1:40:52.21,1:40:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}被我的唾液弄的湿答答的知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:40:58.30,1:40:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害
Dialogue: 2,1:40:59.96,1:41:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很好
Dialogue: 2,1:41:21.40,1:41:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想放进去了？
Dialogue: 2,1:41:25.24,1:41:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我也想放进去
Dialogue: 2,1:41:31.70,1:41:33.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想进去对吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:41:33.25,1:41:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想进去
Dialogue: 2,1:41:41.67,1:41:43.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那来这里
Dialogue: 2,1:41:57.88,1:42:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这里好湿了
Dialogue: 2,1:42:01.79,1:42:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}能进去吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:42:04.06,1:42:05.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}慢慢的
Dialogue: 2,1:42:35.70,1:42:39.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的都不变软呢
Dialogue: 2,1:42:40.05,1:42:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很抱歉
Dialogue: 2,1:42:41.05,1:42:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直硬著呢
Dialogue: 2,1:42:45.01,1:42:46.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}看到课长
Dialogue: 2,1:42:47.03,1:42:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就变得很硬
Dialogue: 2,1:42:48.58,1:42:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}说什么呢
Dialogue: 2,1:42:51.35,1:42:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不行啊
Dialogue: 2,1:42:52.50,1:42:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样怎么工作
Dialogue: 2,1:42:53.76,1:42:54.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起
Dialogue: 2,1:42:55.40,1:42:58.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}怎么办呢？以后看到我就勃起
Dialogue: 2,1:42:58.47,1:43:02.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}工作中怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:43:03.40,1:43:06.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}听著吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:43:06.84,1:43:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}工作的时候满脑子想著打飞机的事
Dialogue: 2,1:43:13.17,1:43:14.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}工作也做不好
Dialogue: 2,1:43:14.47,1:43:18.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对不起
Dialogue: 2,1:43:25.77,1:43:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:43:42.92,1:43:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别停
Dialogue: 2,1:43:50.00,1:43:57.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又是这样，总是让我困扰
Dialogue: 2,1:43:59.49,1:44:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}知道吗自己做的事
Dialogue: 2,1:44:04.17,1:44:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你的鸡儿真的明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:44:09.27,1:44:11.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还一直插呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:44:13.05,1:44:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}不要插的这么大声
Dialogue: 2,1:44:20.18,1:44:21.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:44:34.58,1:44:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:44:42.42,1:44:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}让我去了这么多次
Dialogue: 2,1:44:46.20,1:44:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我忍耐了很久，忍很久了吗？很想射吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:44:52.51,1:44:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真辛苦呢忍耐了这么久
Dialogue: 2,1:44:57.47,1:45:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射了应该很舒服吧
Dialogue: 2,1:45:05.26,1:45:07.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}再多忍耐一会
Dialogue: 2,1:45:08.17,1:45:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忍耐了等等让你射出来
Dialogue: 2,1:45:10.85,1:45:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}咻咻的很舒服的
Dialogue: 2,1:45:17.10,1:45:19.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}对看著我
Dialogue: 2,1:46:03.76,1:46:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只顾自己爽真狡猾
Dialogue: 2,1:46:05.99,1:46:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}换我了
Dialogue: 2,1:46:20.32,1:46:22.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直想跟我做
Dialogue: 2,1:46:26.33,1:46:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直想跟课长做...
Dialogue: 2,1:46:28.56,1:46:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直想跟我做呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:46:39.10,1:46:41.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你知道你在做不对的事吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:46:42.90,1:46:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你真的知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:47:26.85,1:47:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:47:46.76,1:47:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真不妙
Dialogue: 2,1:47:57.71,1:48:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一边kiss一边好好插我
Dialogue: 2,1:48:04.66,1:48:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}快一点
Dialogue: 2,1:48:22.13,1:48:25.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}太舒服了
Dialogue: 2,1:48:25.87,1:48:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}很舒服呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:48:29.23,1:48:30.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害
Dialogue: 2,1:48:58.97,1:49:01.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我正在高潮
Dialogue: 2,1:49:02.50,1:49:04.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}别插这么深
Dialogue: 2,1:49:06.40,1:49:12.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}插这么深又马上要去了
Dialogue: 2,1:49:41.99,1:49:44.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这么想动吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:00.94,1:50:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长我可以亲你吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:04.65,1:50:05.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}可以
Dialogue: 2,1:50:36.21,1:50:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}在里面又变硬了呢
Dialogue: 2,1:50:40.48,1:50:42.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忍不住了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:42.65,1:50:44.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想射吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:44.16,1:50:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想射想的受不了了吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:48.83,1:50:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}已经忍不住了？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:51.64,1:50:53.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}已经极限了？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:53.56,1:50:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那射吧
Dialogue: 2,1:50:56.40,1:50:58.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想射哪呢？
Dialogue: 2,1:50:58.85,1:51:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的胸部...
Dialogue: 2,1:51:01.31,1:51:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想射胸上？
Dialogue: 2,1:51:13.70,1:51:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}龟头变得好大
Dialogue: 2,1:51:53.15,1:51:54.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射在胸上了
Dialogue: 2,1:52:10.00,1:52:11.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好厉害
Dialogue: 2,1:52:24.19,1:52:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}你清爽了？
Dialogue: 2,1:52:28.25,1:52:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我清爽了
Dialogue: 2,1:52:37.37,1:52:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}明天要回东京了
Dialogue: 2,1:52:40.97,1:52:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}睡吧
Dialogue: 2,1:52:49.60,1:52:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}晚安
Dialogue: 2,1:53:04.65,1:53:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}难波
Dialogue: 2,1:53:07.37,1:53:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}新干线的时间是11点
Dialogue: 2,1:53:10.77,1:53:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}差不多该起床整理了
Dialogue: 2,1:53:26.32,1:53:27.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...
Dialogue: 2,1:53:30.12,1:53:33.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}这样没法坐新干线
Dialogue: 2,1:53:37.67,1:53:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没时间了
Dialogue: 2,1:53:39.52,1:53:40.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}抱歉
Dialogue: 2,1:53:41.04,1:53:41.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}但是
Dialogue: 2,1:53:43.52,1:53:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直消不下去
Dialogue: 2,1:53:51.50,1:53:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}只做一下下
Dialogue: 2,1:53:53.60,1:53:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}谢谢
Dialogue: 2,1:53:56.20,1:53:57.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:54:01.35,1:54:03.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一早起来就这么大
Dialogue: 2,1:54:05.15,1:54:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}每天都这样吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:54:14.77,1:54:17.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}早上起来就这样子
Dialogue: 2,1:54:20.97,1:54:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}为什么勃起成这个样子
Dialogue: 2,1:54:23.46,1:54:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}晨勃了...
Dialogue: 2,1:54:25.90,1:54:27.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}昨天太亢奋了
Dialogue: 2,1:54:28.57,1:54:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}上床去
Dialogue: 2,1:54:31.27,1:54:32.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想做对吧
Dialogue: 2,1:54:44.22,1:54:47.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}昨天射了这么多
Dialogue: 2,1:54:47.70,1:54:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还没有满足？
Dialogue: 2,1:54:49.85,1:54:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}抱歉
Dialogue: 2,1:54:51.20,1:54:52.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}勃起的这么大
Dialogue: 2,1:54:54.30,1:54:56.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还想跟课长做...
Dialogue: 2,1:55:20.46,1:55:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}碰到我了你知道吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:55:24.57,1:55:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}一直摩擦著
Dialogue: 2,1:55:32.60,1:55:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}忍耐汁该不会出来了吧？
Dialogue: 2,1:55:43.05,1:55:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}变的这么大
Dialogue: 2,1:55:52.00,1:55:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}乳头想被摸？
Dialogue: 2,1:55:54.05,1:55:56.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想被直接摸...
Dialogue: 2,1:56:01.66,1:56:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}没时间了呢？明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:56:04.02,1:56:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}是，我明白的...
Dialogue: 2,1:56:05.77,1:56:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真的明白吗？
Dialogue: 2,1:56:09.50,1:56:11.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}自己脱了吧
