Dialogue: 2,2:41:46.23,2:41:47.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}也是呢
Dialogue: 2,2:41:51.75,2:41:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来做更多舒服的事吧
Dialogue: 2,2:41:55.70,2:41:57.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还能做吧？
Dialogue: 2,2:41:58.78,2:41:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还想要做...
Dialogue: 2,2:42:00.05,2:42:00.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}和课长...
Dialogue: 2,2:42:02.27,2:42:03.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}来吧
Dialogue: 2,2:42:07.18,2:42:09.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}就是这样
Dialogue: 2,2:42:12.06,2:42:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}舒服？
Dialogue: 2,2:42:14.27,2:42:15.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好舒服
Dialogue: 2,2:42:18.07,2:42:21.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}刚才才射了那么多
Dialogue: 2,2:42:22.22,2:42:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又这样
Dialogue: 2,2:42:30.33,2:42:33.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}积了很多吗？
Dialogue: 2,2:42:34.24,2:42:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}射了又射，射了又射
Dialogue: 2,2:42:37.72,2:42:39.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}如果是课长，我想要射很多
Dialogue: 2,2:42:39.74,2:42:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想射很多吗？多少次都想射
Dialogue: 2,2:42:43.22,2:42:45.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真令人困扰呢
Dialogue: 2,2:42:51.51,2:42:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}好硬
Dialogue: 2,2:42:53.55,2:42:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要去了
Dialogue: 2,2:43:15.40,2:43:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长的小穴这样夹的话我又...
Dialogue: 2,2:43:20.23,2:43:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}小穴自作主张我才不知道呢
Dialogue: 2,2:43:23.81,2:43:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}我又要射了
Dialogue: 2,2:43:26.67,2:43:28.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又要？
Dialogue: 2,2:43:28.97,2:43:31.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想射在胸部上
Dialogue: 2,2:43:31.95,2:43:37.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}想把我全身都弄脏呢
Dialogue: 2,2:43:37.15,2:43:41.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}要射了
Dialogue: 2,2:43:43.57,2:43:45.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}又要射在我身上了
Dialogue: 2,2:44:15.30,2:44:17.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还有对吧？
Dialogue: 2,2:44:51.37,2:44:52.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还能射吗？
Dialogue: 2,2:44:53.68,2:44:54.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}还能射...
Dialogue: 2,2:44:54.88,2:44:56.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}课长...
Dialogue: 2,2:44:56.57,2:44:58.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}真拿你没办法呢
Dialogue: 2,2:44:59.29,2:45:01.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}那来吧
Dialogue: 2,2:45:05.67,2:45:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fad(120,120)}今天一整天都做吧
